751
01:06:05,230 --> 01:06:08,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa memaksanya merawatmu kalau dia tidak mau.</font>

752
01:06:10,800 --> 01:06:11,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo pergi.</font>

753
01:06:30,960 --> 01:06:33,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Kopi dan roti isimu sudah siap.</font>

754
01:06:35,070 --> 01:06:36,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Silakan nikmati.</font>

755
01:06:43,930 --> 01:06:45,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia ke sini lagi.</font>

756
01:06:45,500 --> 01:06:46,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

757
01:06:46,570 --> 01:06:48,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia datang setiap hari di jam yang sama.</font>

758
01:06:48,330 --> 01:06:51,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Kemudian dia memesan roti isi yang paling murah,
